data.description: HORSE PROPERTY at YOUR new desert sanctuary! Nestled in the picturesque city of Cottonwood. This remarkable home is a hidden gem, offering you a sprawling 4.39-acre parcel. This property provides you with ultimate privacy and space to enjoy the beautiful desert landscape. As you step inside, you'll discover a beautifully designed interior that seamlessly combines with the charm of the Southwest. The stunning granite countertops in the spacious kitchen are complemented by stainless steel appliances. Convenience abounds with a spacious two-car garage and your own private water well. A pristine pool area to dive into your own oasis, all while enjoying breathtaking Mingus and Red Rock mountain views or explore the potential for activities including space for you and your beloved horses
